|CK0Prayers to Set require more than just a temporary cost. Set requires
|CK0something greater, an extended bargain. This bargain "reserves" part of
|CK0the priest's HP or SP for a few minutes.
|CK0
|CK0During this time, the health or energy isn't available for other
|CK0prayers, and cannot be healed nor restored. In the "prayers" command,
|CK0these show as the "HPR" and "SPR" costs, short for health and
|CK0spell point reservations.
